OL,6,FWest Midlands Police spent less than
OL,7,F1% of money recovered from the
OL,8,Fproceeds of crime on road safety.
OL,10,FData shared with ITV News Central by
OL,11,FBirmingham Edgbaston MP Preet Gill
OL,12,Fshows only #34,591 was used to tackle
OL,13,Fthe issue, despite the force
OL,14,Frecovering #3,786,232 in 2022-2023.
OL,16,FThe news comes as many across the
OL,17,FMidlands are campaigning for better
OL,18,Froad safety and awareness, after
OL,19,Fmultiple deaths on our roads.
