OL,6,FAmong them is Better Streets for
OL,7,FBirmingham, who say that since last
OL,8,Fyear alone 23 people have died in
OL,9,Ffatal collisions in Birmingham.
OL,11,FThe MP for Edgbaston, Preet Gill, said
OL,12,Fin the last two months alone two of
OL,13,Fher constituents have died in road
OL,14,Faccidents. One of them was just 20
OL,15,Fyears old.
OL,17,F"It's heartbreaking that so many
OL,18,Fpeople in this city have lost loved
OL,19,Fones as a result of dangerous driving.
OL,20,FEveryone should feel safe on our
OL,21,Froads."
