OL,6,FMs Gill said: "Improving road safety
OL,7,Fis an emergency in this city. West
OL,8,FMidlands Police along with
OL,9,FBirmingham's leaders must look at how
OL,10,Fwe can work together to ensure that no
OL,11,Fone else tragically dies on our
OL,12,Fregion's roads."
OL,14,FThe data also shows, from 2017 to
OL,15,F2023, out of #14,438,393 recovered,
OL,16,Fjust #62,346 was allocated to 'road
OL,17,Farms initiatives'.
