OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has backed
OL,7,Fcalls for the declaration of a "road
OL,8,Fsafety emergency", but when asked West
OL,9,FMidlands Police did not directly
OL,10,Frespond to how much money has been
OL,11,Fspent on road safety.
OL,13,FCouncillor Majid Mahmood has written a
OL,14,Fletter to West Midlands Police Chief
OL,15,FConstable Craig Guildford.
OL,17,FHe stated that following the incidents
OL,18,Fin Boldmere yesterday evening and on
OL,19,FCoventry Road this morning: "We have
OL,20,Fnow had 10 fatal collisions on
OL,21,FBirmingham's roads this calendar year."
