OL,6,FMr Mahmood said following information
OL,7,Freceived from the police, the causes
OL,8,Fof the most serious and fatal
OL,9,Fcollisions appear to be largely
OL,10,Frelated to alcohol, drugs, dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving, and nighttime street racing.
OL,13,FHe said a Road Safety Emergency must
OL,14,Fbe declared and has requested the
OL,15,Fimmediate standing up of a Gold
OL,16,FCommand to coordinate a multi-agency
OL,17,Fresponse.
OL,19,FWhen asked, West Midlands Police did
OL,20,Fnot directly respond to how much money
OL,21,Fhas been spent on road safety.
