OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "In the West
OL,7,FMidlands, we have set the goal to
OL,8,Freduce road death and serious injury
OL,9,Fto zero under Vision Zero.
OL,11,F"We are working with communities and
OL,12,Fpartners and are aware of their
OL,13,Fentirely understandable concern.
OL,15,F"Our partnership sees us work with
OL,16,Flocal councils, charities the West
OL,17,FMidlands Combined Authority and others
OL,18,Fto achieve safer roads for everyone.
