OL,6,F"Our proactive approach involves
OL,7,Ffocused operations in key areas,
OL,8,Ftackling the 'fatal four' and
OL,9,Fpreventing harm to the most vulnerable
OL,10,Froad users. The fatal four includes,
OL,11,Fspeeding, drink and drug driving,
OL,12,Fusing a mobile phone while driving and
OL,13,Fnot wearing a seatbelt.
OL,15,F"We will continue our push to Vision
OL,16,FZero but to achieve this goal, we will
OL,17,Fneed the support of all partners,
OL,18,Fcommunities and road users."
